  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18 and over.

          -  Symptoms consistent with a possible acute coronary syndrome per the treating emergency
             physician.

          -  Has an electrocardiogram performed while in the ED.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Acute ST-segment elevation MI.

          -  Patient unable or unwilling to complete follow-up.
      </textblock>
